### set-changed-apps-matrix paths
###   defines the paths apps-matrix-output-from-git-diff.sh will use to detect changes in the repository
###   __app__ is replaced with the current app or \$app
###   The paths use `git pathspec` syntax.
###   `git pathspec` reference: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitglossary#Documentation/gitglossary.txt-aiddefpathspecapathspec

:(glob,top)**/__app__/**
:(glob,top,exclude)**/__app__/deploy/releases/**
